All gold hardware, beautiful fingerboard with block inlays and a potent Mini Humbucker pickup. Guitar has one volume and one tone knob. It comes in an older case that is in decent shape. I bought it without a case but I did not want to ship it without something protecting it. You might want to get a better one after you get it. I took the pick guard bracket off because it was easier for me to play it. When I went to put it back on one of the screws were missing. The one that goes over the side and attaches to the body. In a couple of the pics you will see a black screw in its placed. I only put that screw in there to hold it steady while I was taking the pics. I did not fully screw it in so it has not damaged the wood. I will remove that screw when I ship unless you had rather me leave it in. I might take the pick-guard off when I am shipping so there will not be any movement that might scratch the finish. The guitar is in like new condition in every-way. Plays over the top great. Low, Low playing hours on the gtr. (3?). Sounds great direct into LOGIC and sounds really great coming out of Fender amp. The brass/gold screw will need to be replaced. Prob. cost 5 cents.Please purchase with confidence. I am a 18 year EBAYER with a 100% rating. Good look.
